Dr.XiaowenSongiscurrentlyanAssociateProfessorofMechanicalEngineeringatZhejiangUniversity.ShereceivedherB.Sc.inComputationalMathematicsfromFudanUniversityin1989,followedbyaM.S.degreeinComputationalGeometry&amp;ComputerGraphicsandaPh.D.degreeinMechanicalEngineeringfromZhejiangUniversityin1992and1996,respectively.FromNov.2001toFeb.2003,shestudiedattheDepartmentofComputerScience,BrighamYoungUniversity,U.S.A.asavisitingscholar.SheisarecipientofZhejiangUniversityoutstandingfacultyaward,andservesasamemberofthereviewingpanelofResearchStartupFundingforOverseaReturnees,ChineseNationalMinistryofEducation(MOE).Dr.SongisamemberofChineseMechanicalEngineeringSociety,andservesasthedeputysecretary-generalof&nbsp;MoldDesignCommittee&nbsp;at&nbsp;theDesignBranchofChineseMechanicalEngineeringSociety.Inaddition,sheisacorememberoftheKeyInnovationTeamonScienceandTechnologyofZhejiangProvince.

